	<h1 class="title">万圣节营销，看看这几家公司是怎么玩的</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/8/small/8.jpg?1448336190" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">马宁忆</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-10-30 08:26:04 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/3149/medium/3149.jpg?1436636747" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


